----------------------------------------------------------------------

Copyright and License of the scheme script 'nt2w' is given in that file.
The original name of that file is 'text2wave', which is available with
'festival' package. The modifications made to the file are :
1. File name changed.
2. The second line of the script changed to :-
   "true" ; exec /usr/bin/festival --script $0 $*

If next version of 'festival' fix this problem, 'nt2w' will be removed from 
this package.
----------------------------------------------------------------------


Installation
-=-=-=-=-=-=

1. Login as 'root'
2. run install.sh script, to run :

	$./install.sh

(You must install 'festival' and 'sox' packages)


Usage
=-=-=

Enter 'swaram' command from terminal.

